'''Potato Potahto''' ni filime yo gusetsa y’urukundo yo muri [[Gana]]  yo muri 2017 yakozwe na  Shirley Frimpong-Manso ivuga amateka yo gutandukana muri societe y'uburengerazuba bwa [[Afurika|Afrika]] nuburyo bigoye<ref>https://www.filmafrica.org/film-africa-events/potato-potahto/</ref>.<ref>https://www.graphic.com.gh/entertainment/showbiz-news/shirley-frimpong-manso-s-potato-potahto-makes-it-to-netflix.html</ref>

== Umugambi ==
Potato Potahto ni firime yo gusetsa yo muri [[Gana]]-[[Nigeriya]] ikurikira ubuzima bwabafatanyabikorwa babiri bahatirwa kubana ubuzima bwabo munzu imwe nyuma yo gutandukana<ref>https://www.telerama.fr/cinema/films/potato-potahto,n6579913.php</ref>.  

== Umusaruro ==
Iyi filime ifatanije n’amasosiyete yo muri [[Nijeriya]] Ascend Studios, ku ya 19 Mata Imyidagaduro Virgo Sun Ltd na Lufodo Productions ikaba yari iyobowe n’umukinnyi wa firime wo muri [[Gana]], Shirley Frimpong-Manso <ref>https://africanmoviestar.com/2020/potato-potahto/</ref>. Irerekana ibintu by'akajagari bibaho iyo abashakanye batanye bagumye hamwe murugo rwabashakanye, buri wese afata ubufasha bushimishije bwabahuje igitsina<ref>https://www.allocine.fr/film/fichefilm_gen_cfilm=293250.html</ref>.  Iyi filime yafashwe mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri, ku bufatanye n’abatunganya amafilime yo muri [[Suwede]], [[Bufaransa|Abafaransa]], [[Bwongereza|Abongereza]], [[Nijeriya]] na [[Gana]]<ref>https://nollywoodpost.com/post/potato-potahto-a-comedic-take-on-divorce</ref>. 

