== Kwakira ==
Ibirayi Potahto yakiriwe neza na rubanda, kubera intsinzi Shirley Frimpong-Manso yagezeho mbere<ref>https://www.bellanaija.com/2017/05/potato-potahto-cannes-film-festival-premiere/</ref>. Filime yagaragaye 7.9 nabakoresha kuri Nollywood Reinvented<ref>https://www.theghanareport.com/shirley-frimpong-mansos-potato-potahto-to-stream-on-netflix-this-december/</ref>.  Ibirayi Potahto yabonye imyiyerekano mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes, Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya Durban ndetse n’Iserukiramuco rya Filimi [[Bwongereza|ry’Abongereza]].<ref>http://africanwomenincinema.blogspot.com/2018/10/ndiva-womens-film-festival-2018-potato.html</ref> Iyi filime kandi yagaragaye mu rwego rwo gutoranya iserukiramuco rya Filime [[Afurika]] kuva ku ya 27 Ukwakira kugeza 5 Ugushyingo. Ukuboza 2019, Potato Potahto yongewe kumugaragaro kurutonde rwa Netflix<ref>https://www.pulse.ng/entertainment/movies/potato-potahto-how-shirley-frimpong-manso-put-a-hilarious-spin-on-divorce/95zl2c3</ref>.

